Notes for building on various platforms


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
generic POSIX:

Outputs to file descriptor.  Future: ncurses, SDL

Recommended way to build:
make


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Kobo:

Cross-compiles and outputs to file descriptor.  Future: framebuffer

Recommended way to build:
OCHER_UI_FD=1 OCHER_UI_MX50=0 TARGET=kobo make


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Windows:

Builds under Cygwin as a POSIX app.
May someday think about WIN32 proper.

Recommended way to build:
make


